{"tid":2137834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［中立撚都表態］中國背離開放之路　瑞士外長：西方國家將果斷回應","createTime":"2020-08-03T08:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T12:15:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea2e002347659a1164b214e62ebfa55289f6508","tid":2137834,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"瑞士外交部長凱西斯（Ignazio Cassis）周日向媒體表示，中國正背離開放之路，還說中國若依然故我，西方國家將更加果斷地做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，凱西斯向周報《星期展望》（SonntagsBlick）表示，中國政治自由化與經濟自由化未成正比，且中國侵犯人權的情事日趨嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n凱西斯說：「我們看見中國正背離開放之路。」<br />\n<br />\n「這表示瑞士也必須更加堅定地捍衛自身利益與價值，例如藉由強化國際法及多邊體系達成。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200803/Y76IEXJHIFFALGIRNJI4MF32UI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200803%2FY76IEXJHIFFALGIRNJI4MF32UI%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=79ed2dc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200803%2FY76IEXJHIFFALGIRNJI4MF32UI%2F&h=cac04497\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200803/Y76IEXJHIFFALGIRNJI4MF32UI/</a>"},{"pid":"1cd260b159cf92e85abcfd0c860fcf22253eebc3","tid":2137834,"uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"歐洲歸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ea83d65dd69fbb5d70d4579891e98322c696e7","tid":2137834,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d90afa4b6d3977ba38a4799353678c86d10785","tid":2137834,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislik